npm init

npm i express morgan nodemon ejs body-parser dotenv mongoose axios

* Express used to rapidly develope the node application
* Morgan used to log a message when we make request every time
* Nodemon used to automatically restart the server when we give some changes in program
* EJS is a template engine for this project its allows you to create dynamic HTML.
* What Is Body-parser?   Express body-parser is an npm module used to process data sent in an HTTP request body. It provides four express middleware for parsing JSON, Text, URL-encoded, and raw data sets over an HTTP request body.
* dotenv is the module allows you to separate the secrete from your source code.
mongoose using this module we are going to connect mongoDB
* axios this library allows easy to make a request in express application